    <item>
      <title>Text</title>
      <link>/taking-train-to-amms/44841881</link>
      <guid>/taking-train-to-amms/44841881</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 18:31:27 GMT</pubDate>
      <description><![CDATA[<p>i&#39;ve begun to write daily. 4 days so far. i wonder if it will last. i try to do it in the morning. i tried it at night but i couldn&#39;t sleep afterwards. it must wake up the mind.</p>

<p>i&#39;ve been thinking of starting a website for just this. an indicator to show that you are online and others are there too. i plan to reuse a domain for this. it can be quite simple. a notepad but feel free to bring your own.</p>

<p>&quot;most days we gather here at 9am to write for 1 hour&quot;</p>

<p>[3 runners pass by in the foggy park. in the same outfit. through the bare trees]</p>

<p>i want to ground myself in my website. i&#39;m not really sure what this means yet but i hope to find out. i thought grounding myself had to do with place but i&#39;m not so sure anymore. maybe a site can be grounding. a site for grounding. as a way to learn more about yourself and in turn my relationship with others</p>]]></description>
    </item>
